A company transitioning from a B2B to a combined B2B and B2C business model faced scalability issues, such as contradictory customer information and ineffective marketing segmentation. To address these challenges, they sought CRM solutions and decided on Odoo CRM after a thorough evaluation. The implementation included enhancements like Amazon SQS for improved system communication and a Google Chrome extension using Javascript, Vue.js, and GPT chat completions API for AI-driven email template generation. These measures successfully streamlined operations and met the company's needs.

